{"tid":2289181,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］支聯會以底價投得維園三個檔位後 隨即被食環署抽起競標並拒絕透露原因","createTime":"2020-11-17T05:31:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T06:02:23.000Z","uid":22556,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4248501c91e29703d630fd9c3e3260e31a9d77d8","tid":2289181,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T05:31:52.000Z","msg":"支聯會秘書蔡耀昌今早親身到場投標，並分別以底價投得近天后的第1、2及8號攤位，惟該會在競得攤位後，隨即被食環署抽起競標，聲稱需取得更多資料，才決定其競標是否成立，是支聯會過去參加競投30年來，歷來首被打壓，蔡批評事件是政治打壓。<br />\n<br />\n蔡耀昌批評，其他在場商家成功競標後均順利簽約，惟只有支聯會被單獨抽出來處理，故有理由相信有關安排具針對性，且有很強烈的政治因素，對此感到強烈不滿，強調會按食環署回覆再作跟進行動。蔡續指，支聯會過去30年都有參加競投，去年亦有投得攤位售賣「自由花」，強調該會有處理濕貨經驗，「睇唔到支聯會繼續工作有任何問題」，認為今次明顯是以他個人或組織身份作阻撓，質疑「今時今日食環署係咪仲依法辦事呢？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201117/HCJS34MDPBBN7LJI5JPA6JTUMM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3PpLMa7WFWiMPWjpmTbVF1O0LwYURD01ZqKSoAkXJjuu0pWT1glU7EaA4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201117%2FHCJS34MDPBBN7LJI5JPA6JTUMM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3PpLMa7WFWiMPWjpmTbVF1O0LwYURD01ZqKSoAkXJjuu0pWT1glU7EaA4&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM4wu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=1e6a7d94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201117%2FHCJS34MDPBBN7LJI5JPA6JTUMM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3PpLMa7WFWiMPWjpmTbVF1O0LwYURD01ZqKSoAkXJjuu0pWT1glU7EaA4&h=3d908f13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201117/HCJS34MDPBBN7LJI5JPA6JTUMM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3PpLMa7WFWiMPWjpmTbVF1O0LwYURD01ZqKSoAkXJjuu0pWT1glU7EaA4</a>"},{"pid":"338c4